  "changelogHtml": "<h3 id=\"1.2.0-rc01\" data-text=\"Version 1.2.0-rc01\" tabindex=\"-1\">Version 1.2.0-rc01</h3>\n<p>June 15, 2022</p>\n<p><code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">androidx.compose.material:material-*:1.2.0-rc01</code> is released. <a href=\"https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/support/+log/5973fd35e79471563d11a6776b6a1816b1e33409..2d8badfd263991345376562fc0f247bc76ca6312/compose/material\">Version 1.2.0-rc01 contains these commits.</a></p>\n<p><strong>API Changes</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Interfaces in compose libraries are now built using jdk8 default interface methods (<a href=\"https://android-review.googlesource.com/#/q/I5bcf197603f66ec66177c98c01c3fe4868d60997\">I5bcf1</a>)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Bug Fixes</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Updates badge with leading icon tab to affix badge to the label instead of the icon. (<a href=\"https://android-review.googlesource.com/#/q/I90993b49d4804875e9e3dfe95b5ff715825063a5\">I90993</a>)</li>\n</ul>",
